<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Khawvel lopina leh hawihna I hawllai hin,
 Lungdawnna, lungzinnan ei tuomvel;
 Mahleh kinepnan eihun zuon zelin atii,
 Zie khawvel ahin thamuonna ding ka mu puoi.

[V2]
 Thamuonna leh nawpna neitu I Lal Isu'n,
 &quot;Ka kawmah hung unla hung zilun atii;
 Ka namkawl anuoma ka puokle a zang hi,
 Na thagau adingin chawlhdamna hun piengka.&quot;

[V3]
 2. Khawvel duhamna chu milim hona ahi,
 Dangka ngaihnat gitloh bul ahi;
 Khawvel lopina, hauhna, gitloh nawpna te,
 A tawpna chu kumsawt Gawtmun meidil ahi.

[V4]
 3. Ka thilin khawvel lopina azam viel ie,
 A hawihna haw pak bangin alun;
 Ka Hukdampa phatna leh a mel a lieh zo,
 Aw Isu na mel hawihtak chu eimuh sakin.

[V5]
 4. Ka hun zuon hi Lalpa nangmai nawpna na hi,
 Chawlhdamna leh puokgik kei dawntu;
 Ka mu ta ie! damna, leh muonna, Lal Isu,
 Kumsawt in kipahna pak bang lun zing tan a.</lyrics>
<title>Thamuonna Leh Nawpna</title>
</song>